    "Name": "Harasser (LRM)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Harasser Missile Platform (LRM)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>11/18 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>120 ICE</color></b>\n\nThe Harasser is a low-cost hover tank equipped with a variety of missile launchers that was widely integrated into Galleon Light Tank units in the Free Worlds League.\n\nOne of the most common variants, the 2821 version replaces the pair of SRM-6s with a single LRM-10 launcher and two additional tons of ammunition, enabling the Harasser to provide long-range fire support while using its speed to keep out of harm's way.",
